INkantolo eNkulu yaseMadadeni igwebe uMbuyiseni Mthembu (37) ngoMsombuluko. NgoSepthemba 2017, uMthembu nayehamba nabo batheleka endaweni yakwaFedility ngemuva kwehora lesishiyagalolunye. Kuthiwa bafike bakhomba onogada ngezibhamu, babaphoqa ukuthi babatshengise izikhiye zalapho kuhlala khona imali. Ngenkathi sebezitholile bavula bayithatha base bebaleka nemali enguR12 million. Icala lokuphanga lavulwa esiteshini samaphoyisa eVryheid. Idokodo lecala labe selidluliselwa koKlebe ophikweni oluphenya ngamacala abucayi. UCaptain Simphiwe Mhlongo woKlebe uthe abasolwa abahlanu okunguPhakamani Hadebe (32), Mnikeni Khohlwezakhe Majozi (59), Thembokwakhe Robert Nzama (41), Zakhele Ernesty Xulu (32) noMthembu babe sebeboshwa. “OKlebe bakwazi ukuthola imali enguR700 000 ngenkathi bebopha abasolwa,” kusho uMhlongo. Uthe abasolwa ababili okunguMajozi noNzama babaleka ngemuva kokuphuma ngebheyili kaR30 000. “Kwakhishwa incwadi egunyaza ukuthi beboshwe. Okwamanje abakatholakali kodwa amaphoyisa aphansi phezulu ayabathungatha,” kusho uMhlongo.